  "detailed_description": "<h1>玩法交流＆BUG反馈</h1><p>问题反馈及玩法讨论请加入官方QQ群：734117642</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>在游戏中你能感受到“庄周梦蝶”的中式浪漫，在一幅幅水墨画卷般的关卡中，将“汉字”释义与场景、物品相结合，创作出饱含五千年中华文化底蕴的特色谜题。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083600/extras/32aa50ea0014d69778d08b14d78f63f5.avif?t=1757063676\" width=600 height=300 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【脑洞大开的汉字谜题】</h2>游戏场景中许多物体可以转化为对应含义的字，通过汉字结构的拆分与重组，变为新的字。<br>新的文字，又意味着可以成为新的物品。<br>通过操作，玩家们可以改变游戏中原有世界的构造，突破原本不可能逾越的障碍。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083600/extras/25fb7da62e7ca4a50b9786f2080c3b82.poster.avif?t=1757063676\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083600/extras/25fb7da62e7ca4a50b9786f2080c3b82.webm?t=1757063676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083600/extras/25fb7da62e7ca4a50b9786f2080c3b82.mp4?t=1757063676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【趣味横生的语文课】</h2>在解谜的过程中，重新领会一个个汉字背后的含义，一个个典故所蕴含的古老文化思想，重温在儿时学习汉字、诗词、典故时，因五千年悠长岁月沉淀所带来的感动。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083600/extras/ee5520c9ebdd634576c4e8d07433e0ad.poster.avif?t=1757063676\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083600/extras/ee5520c9ebdd634576c4e8d07433e0ad.webm?t=1757063676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083600/extras/ee5520c9ebdd634576c4e8d07433e0ad.mp4?t=1757063676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【文艺而充满回忆的山水画】</h2>在学生时代的语文和历史教材中，有许许多多的国画插图，都成为<br>在《梦蝶》里，各种美术设定忠实重现了那种泼墨山水的氛围。<br>无论是总角之龄的孩童，还是绿丝万条的垂柳，都让人不禁回忆起童年。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083600/extras/bd9b8b9f06dbef84d57c782f17da36c4.poster.avif?t=1757063676\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083600/extras/bd9b8b9f06dbef84d57c782f17da36c4.webm?t=1757063676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083600/extras/bd9b8b9f06dbef84d57c782f17da36c4.mp4?t=1757063676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【藏于梦中的奇幻隐世】</h2>游戏描绘了一个名为“栖云洲”的神秘奇幻世界，蝴蝶指引，仙人隐居的背后，存在着不为常世所知的秘密。与制作组另一款游戏《栖云异梦》共享世界观，在穿梭古今的不同故事中，一起还原幻境真相。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083600/extras/563820e39c0a8c94e2581eba11fb4463.poster.avif?t=1757063676\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083600/extras/563820e39c0a8c94e2581eba11fb4463.webm?t=1757063676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083600/extras/563820e39c0a8c94e2581eba11fb4463.mp4?t=1757063676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
